<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: heavy club -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_HeavyClub.label>重型棍棒</VWE_MeleeWeapon_HeavyClub.label>
  <!-- EN: A large, two handed, shaped stick for bashing enemies. Extreme weight at the end of this tool allows user to crush flesh and bones alike, leaving enemies maimed, paralysed and often dead. -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_HeavyClub.description>一根大号的双手握持的棍棒，用来敲砸敌人。该武器末端的重物使使用者轻松能够粉碎肉体和骨骼，将敌人打残、瘫痪并死亡。</VWE_MeleeWeapon_HeavyClub.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_HeavyClub.tools.handle.label>握柄</VWE_MeleeWeapon_HeavyClub.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_HeavyClub.tools.head.label>棍头</VWE_MeleeWeapon_HeavyClub.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: light club -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_LightClub.label>轻型棍棒</VWE_MeleeWeapon_LightClub.label>
  <!-- EN: A small, one handed club. Whilst it's fast to swing, it is not going to cause tremendous damage due to its low weight and short length. -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_LightClub.description>小巧的单手棍棒，虽然挥舞起来速度很快，但重量小，长度也短，不能造成多大的伤害。</VWE_MeleeWeapon_LightClub.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_LightClub.tools.handle.label>握柄</VWE_MeleeWeapon_LightClub.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_LightClub.tools.head.label>棍头</VWE_MeleeWeapon_LightClub.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: shiv -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Shiv.label>小刀</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Shiv.label>
  <!-- EN: One of mankind's oldest manufactured objects. A shiv is a short but sharp piece of rock or metal with a small handle. -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Shiv.description>人类最古老的武器之一。小刀是一种短而尖锐的岩石或金属片，有一截很短的握柄。</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Shiv.description>
  <!-- EN: blade -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Shiv.tools.blade.label>刀刃</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Shiv.tools.blade.label>
  <!-- EN: point -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Shiv.tools.point.label>刀尖</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Shiv.tools.point.label>
  
  <!-- EN: tribal axe -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_TribalAxe.label>部落斧</VWE_MeleeWeapon_TribalAxe.label>
  <!-- EN: A sharp piece of rock mounted on a sturdy piece of wood. Often used as a tool, it has been recorded that tribal axes also served as a great weapon due to their small size and ability to inflict deep wounds. -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_TribalAxe.description>一块安装在坚固的木头上的锋利的石头。常常当作工具使用。因为它的体积小，而且能够造成很深的伤口，也同时被当作一种不错的武器。</VWE_MeleeWeapon_TribalAxe.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_TribalAxe.tools.handle.label>握柄</VWE_MeleeWeapon_TribalAxe.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: edge -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_TribalAxe.tools.edge.label>斧刃</VWE_MeleeWeapon_TribalAxe.tools.edge.label>
  
</LanguageData>